Package: categorical
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Specific MCA + HCPC with Geometric Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Raymond", "Li", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "91818244+raymondli-me@users.noreply.github.com")
Description: Base-R specific Multiple Correspondence Analysis with HCPC clustering,
    Benzecri correction, Haberman adjusted residuals, geometric typicality tests,
    correlation-ratio (eta^2) permutation tests, bootstrap confidence ellipses
    (centroid or top-k signature), content-based cluster labelling, enriched master
    tables, and configurable base-graphics maps.
    No dependencies for the statistics.
